content: It is good enough for its purpose. This app it's not like a typically game for kids, with rewards and other medals.

Tried several similar apps and this one wins through color options and ease of use. Love that it doesn't correct the kid for drawing outside the lines as miss 4 was getting frustrated with other apps that wouldn't let you progress until you did it exactly 'right'.
I feel this is a way of putting in adds. I wish there was a way to lock this out.
Four year old granddaughter is really enjoying it! It would be nice if it remembered your settings, instead of having to reset every time! ðŸ˜©
Great app but not ment for samsung tab 3  no voice or music just button confirmation sound

I like that my son can trace but the voice feature was a big plus for me. Unfortunately, the voice feature has stopped working a little after I bought the app. It was helping him so much. Well they already have my money so good for them.

Praise your children for their efforts and accomplishments, and encourage them to do better each time.  DON"T TELL THEM about the shake-to-erase option unless you want to buy a new tablet.  I would like it more if it had a cursive option, and the names of the shapes were spoken like they do with the letters.
